<body>

<h1>

    This page contains a couple of HTML forms that GET and POST to the
    REST API provided by your project.

</h1>

<h2>
    These forms let you interact with the simple key/value REST API that
    is created by the project archetype.
</h2>

<div>
    <form action="flights">
        <b>Name of the airline</b> <input name="name" type="text" size="25" title="AirlineName"/>
        <input type="submit" value="Get all the flights"/>
    </form>
</div>

<div>
    <form method="post" action="flights?name=Delta">
    <b><u>Create a new Flight:</u></b><br>
        <table>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right">Name of the Airline:</th><td><input name="name" type="text" size="25" title="Airline Name"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right">Flight Number:</th><td><input name="flightNumber" type="text" size="25" title="Flight Number"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right">Source:</th><td><input name="src" type="text" size="25" title="Source Airport Code"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right"> Depart Time:</th><td><input name="departTime" type="text" size="25" title="Depart Time"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right"> Destination:</th><td><input name="dest" type="text" size="25" title="Destination Airport Code"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right"> Arrival Time:</th><td><input name="arriveTime" type="text" size="25" title="Arrival Time"/></td></tr>
        </table>
        <input type="submit" value="Create"/>
    </form>
</div>

<div>
    <form action="flights">
        <table>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right">Name of the Airline:</th><td><input name="name" type="text" size="25" title="Airline Name"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right">Source:</th><td><input name="src" type="text" size="25" title="Source Airport Code"/></td></tr>
            <tr><th style="text-align: right"> Destination:</th><td><input name="dest" type="text" size="25" title="Destination Airport Code"/></td></tr>
        </table>
        <input type="submit" value="Search"/>
    </form>
</div>

</body>
</html>